absurd-paste-client

Usage: apc [(-f|--file FILENAME) | --stdin | FILES...] [-s|--service SERVICE] 
           [-l|--language LANGUAGE] [-e|--expires EXPIRES] 
           [-E|--expiretimes SERVICE] [-S|--services] [-L|--languages SERVICE] 
           [-d|--debug]
  The (mostly) absurd paste client AKA apc

Available options:
  -f,--file FILENAME       Input file
  --stdin                  Paste from stdin
  -s,--service SERVICE     Paste service to use
  -l,--language LANGUAGE   language for syntax highlighting
  -e,--expires EXPIRES     How long before paste expires
  -E,--expiretimes SERVICE list supported expiretimes for SERVICE
  -S,--services            list supported services
  -L,--languages SERVICE   list supported languages for SERVICE
  -d,--debug               Enable debug mode
  -h,--help                Show this help text
